Nico and Dani;;70;;87;;R;;Chronicles the summer of 2 teenage boys who test the limits of their friendship while discovering much about themselves. Nico and Dani are left on their own at a beach house for a few days; late night dates and parties are the order of the day until it appears that their respective sexual awakenings are leading them in different directions.;;Drama;;Cesc Gay;;2000;;Fernando Ramallo,Jordi Vilches,Marieta Orozco,Esther Nubiola,Chisco Amado,Ana Gracia,Myriam Mézières;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nico_and_dani